\c 23 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 23\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Waaqayyo Tiksee Gaarii Dha (Faarfannaa Daawit)
\m \bd 1\bd* Waaqayyo tiksee koo ti, ani homaa hin dhabu.
\m \bd 2\bd* Inni marga lalisaa keessa akkan boqodhu in godha, gara laga itti aara galfataniittis na geessa.
\m \bd 3\bd* inni lubbuu anatti in deebisa, maqaa isaatiif jedhee daandii qajeelaa irra na geggeessa.
\m \bd 4\bd* Ani bowwaa dukkanaa'aa sodaachisaa keessa yoon adeeme iyyuu, hamaan anatti dhufa jedhee hin sodaadhu; ati anaa wajjin jirta, uleen keetii fi dhaabbanni kee ana in jajjabeessu. 
\m \bd 5\bd* Utuma warri na cunqursan ilaalanii, ati maaddii anaaf in dhi'eessita mataa koos dhadhaa ejersaa in dibda, xoofoon koos guutee irra in dhangala'a.
\m \bd 6\bd* eyyee, bara jireenya koo hundumaatti gaarummaan kee fi arjummaan kee ana duukaa in bu'u; guyyoota kana hundumaafis mana Waaqayyoo keessa nan jiraadha.
